summary: A fairly basic player home set inside a mountain near Whiterun, quick access to Whiterun
descriptionHtml:
Description

Just a home I made for myself, I meant to completely finish it to my liking before releasing it to the public.  But i'm not sure if I will ever be completely happy with it.  So here it is, hopefully I'll update it with some improvements soon.
